OL,3,CRichard Ashcroft heading back home for
OL,4,Chuge Wigan shows
OL,6,FFormer frontman of The Verve, Richard
OL,7,FAshcroft says he has been trying for
OL,8,Fyears to play a gig in his hometown of
OL,9,FWigan but there wasn't the right venue.
OL,11,FRichard is playing two concerts at
OL,12,FRobin Park Arena in July.
OL,14,FIt will be the first time he's played
OL,15,Fin his hometown since The Verve's
OL,16,Fhistoric gig at Haigh Hall, which saw
OL,17,Fa crowd of 33,000 fans.
