OL,3,CRichard Ashcroft heading back home for
OL,4,Chuge Wigan shows
OL,6,FRichard told ITV news: "I didn't
OL,7,Freally want to do Haigh Hall again, on
OL,8,Fmy own, because I'm a bit old school,
OL,9,Fand we did it, I'm not sure I want to
OL,10,Fre-live something, I want to do
OL,11,Fsomething fresh.
OL,13,F"The guys at Wigan Warriors, were the
OL,14,Ffirst to give a positive response,
OL,15,Fsaying 'yeah, we'll put this on, and
OL,16,Fwe can do it'."
