OL,3,CRichard Ashcroft heading back home for
OL,4,Chuge Wigan shows
OL,6,FWhen tickets went on sale, for one gig
OL,7,Finitially, on Saturday 20 July, they
OL,8,Fsold out in less than 24 hours, so
OL,9,Fanother gig was added for the
OL,10,Ffollowing night.
OL,12,FRichard has a strong north west
OL,13,Fpresence in his support bands across
OL,14,Fthe two nights, including Scouse bands
OL,15,FCast, The Zutons and Red Rum Club, and
OL,16,Flocal Wigan band The Stanleys.
