OL,3,CRichard Ashcroft heading back home for
OL,4,Chuge Wigan shows
OL,6,FHe also told ITV Granada the things he
OL,7,Fmisses about his hometown, in
OL,8,Fparticular the interaction in the
OL,9,Fshops: "It's the little things that I
OL,10,Fmiss more than anything, just the way
OL,11,Fpeople call you 'luv', for example
OL,12,Fwhen you're buying a bag of chips.
OL,14,FSmiling, Richard said: "Me and my wife
OL,15,Fhave this debate, because wherever I
OL,16,Fam in the world, if someone says
OL,17,F'where are you from?' I always say 'a
OL,18,Ftown called Wigan not far from
OL,19,FManchester and Liverpool'
