OL,6,FMy wife thinks they mean where I'm
OL,7,Fliving now, but I always think where
OL,8,Fyou're from is where you were born."
OL,10,FRichard Ashcroft has won two Ivor
OL,11,FNovello awards, one for Songwriter of
OL,12,Fthe Year in 1998 and the other for
OL,13,FOutstanding Contribution to British
OL,14,FMusic in 2019.
OL,16,FAt the Live 8 concert in London in
OL,17,F2005, Coldplay's Chris Martin called
OL,18,Fhim "the best singer in the world".
