OL,6,FRichard Ashcroft was lead vocalist
OL,7,Fwith The Verve, alongside guitarist
OL,8,FNick McCabe, bass guitarist Simon
OL,9,FJones and drummer Peter Salisbury.
OL,11,FAshcroft, Jones and Salisbury knew
OL,12,Feach other at school, but met Nick
OL,13,FMcCabe at Winstanley College, and the
OL,14,Fband was formed in 1990.
OL,16,FThe Verve released one of the biggest
OL,17,Falbums of the era in the shape of
OL,18,F'Urban Hymns' - the UK's 18th biggest
OL,19,Fselling album of all-time.
