OL,3,CRichard Ashcroft heading back home for
OL,4,Chuge Wigan shows
OL,6,FIn 1998, the band won two Brit Awards,
OL,7,Fwinning Best British Group, appeared
OL,8,Fon the cover of Rolling Stone in
OL,9,FMarch, and in February 1999, "Bitter
OL,10,FSweet Symphony" was nominated for the
OL,11,FGrammy Award for Best Rock Song.
OL,13,FTwo months after that they split up,
OL,14,Fdue to "internal conflicts."
OL,16,FThe venue for Richard's homecoming
OL,17,Fgigs, Robin Park Arena, Wigan
OL,18,FWarriors' new multi-million pound
OL,19,Ffacility, built in association with
OL,20,FWigan council.
